{"type":null,"faqId":32765,"title":"如何让手机不给降噪耳机充电","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1、手机插上主动降噪耳机后，手机会自动给耳机充电。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2、如果您不想让手机给耳机充电，按住AM180主动降噪耳机上的圆形按钮，然后再把耳机插入到手机，等一秒钟后再松开按钮。这时充电灯不再亮了，手机此时就不会给降噪耳机充电。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3、但此时耳机的麦克风也不能够拾音。因此如果您只是用耳机听音乐，是可以用这个方法的。但是如果要用耳机打电话，请重新插拔耳机后使用。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7467","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748403000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":165,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"降噪耳机,充电","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}